Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,智花說她甚麼時候到？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.28,0:00:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她沒說甚麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是第一次上這兒來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,認識路嗎？知道怎樣換車嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英你就不擔心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是她自己要來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有麻煩的話她打個電話來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  拜託你們去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  沙英學姐你不是得守在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  回來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她還沒到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  打個電話去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了不用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:46.15,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（姐姐）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:49.15,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（姐姐～）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  莫…莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.40,0:00:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非那就是智花？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是智花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我是想確認一下是不是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是智花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.74,0:01:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請恕我失禮  居然站在這裡說話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.58,0:01:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  忘記說了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是沙英的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.15,0:01:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別做傻事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我從大門進來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你的屋子不也亂得可以嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還一點都不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可愛就不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:03:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不喜歡小孩子的那一套
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為這樣才會連個男朋友都找不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不過是個畢業班的學生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  這和姐姐沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在去沏茶來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,智花還真是個可愛的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是由乃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是宮子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說我說  你有男朋友了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,純粹是我在單相思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歌舞伎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,201是我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,202是小宮的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？大家都是一個人生活的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  聖誕樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人生活是個甚麼感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很辛苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最初發現甚麼都必須自己做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:04:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才覺得我之前有多麼依賴父母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  我是覺得這樣很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡這房間的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎隨時來參觀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡這樣的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吊床啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,工作的桌子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這才有美術家的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宮子也是自己做飯吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不太做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乾貨可是很不錯的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跑得很慢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:30.97,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：日語中容易變質和跑得快是同一個詞組，\N所以宮子說乾貨“跑得慢”）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跑得慢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在家我也常做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐連火候都掌握不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什錦煎餅做成甚麼形狀都無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡做飯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想能快點一個人生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人生活可沒那麼輕鬆的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就比如早上可得自己起來的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  沙英經常早上來叫醒我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我早上老是起不來  沙英真幫我大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦  你居然不承認曾經因為大意而遲到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果真就在學校的門前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,徒步大概15秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你看夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,智花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說了不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了放假的時候不讓進的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是姐姐的教室？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很普通的教室嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有其他學科的授課要進行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是理所當然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  要看的你也看了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,智花也喜歡美術甚麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不大喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我的畫兒畫得很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我更喜歡音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或是家政課甚麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀大家  這是幹甚麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  她是我妹妹智花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她說無論如何想參觀一下學校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在多大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上國三
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢業生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是想來山吹高中嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們先回去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  太遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我本想把素描用的那些服裝也給她展示一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我們這正要去買東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  祝大家聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  發現個奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這人是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火星來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是校長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走了走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太搞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,BERRY店也好多人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聖誕老人出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校長？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聖誕老人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡有五個渴望得到禮物的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有五個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:10.75,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（Camera mode）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓我也拍一張嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Merry X'mas
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我將愛和幸福送入大家的家中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？是剛才那位老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給  蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  請進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  真是豪華的聖誕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚可以盡情地吃蛋糕對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師也請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師  你那衣服是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是我親手做的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了  Bravo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,智花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:08:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有這麼個可愛的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻從來不曾提半句呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  不不…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不怎麼可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了  姐妹間不可以吵架喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我還要到下一家去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說很想留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？就要回去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聖誕少女是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我差不多回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也吃得很飽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？大家都要回去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆也好久沒見著了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不要我們再當電燈泡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想太多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓我住你這兒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要來這裡的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:09:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都通過短訊啊傳真啊信件啊告訴過姐姐無數次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可她連個回音都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐一定只是不好意思而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  她也不大說自己家裡的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  她可能是想獨佔智花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後  在捉弄自己喜歡的人的心理的作用下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不可能是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不然她可以對我更好些的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因為她就是個不坦率的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是上沙英學姐那裡去一趟比較好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的姐姐撂一旁去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我們在這裡弄得乒乓響
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如此或許沙英學姐也會很在意地上來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,引誘作戰法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是從小的開始出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說智花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了不要了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英說智花不在她很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起來玩大貧民吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只三個人玩太沒氣氛了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  來吧來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我出完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐又是大貧民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…變成了這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說回來  為甚麼吵架啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為姐姐小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不等價交易？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就說了姐姐不要做多餘的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,智花  好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼是多餘的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想要姐姐的簽名…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想在朋友面前炫耀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我給你簽行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了給你簽了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才被拒絕的那一刻開始我的熱情就消退了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好記仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,簽名甚麼的給她就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐妹真是不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  智花也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我沒睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,智花你明天不還要早起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別在這鬧彆扭了  早點睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？智花要上哪裡去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  老早就和搬來這裡的朋友約好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Xmas Eve  完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「12月25日  再見了梅老師」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睡過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:11:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  弄醒你們了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  智花是要出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  和朋友約好見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  舞濱離這裡多遠？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:23.23,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：舞浜(maihama)，千葉縣浦安市某車站名）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  算了  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我打電話去問好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  多謝你們的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉急急忙忙地就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我還會傳簡訊來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  幫我收拾睡衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我真過得很開心  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一大早就吵吵嚷嚷的  累不累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚大貧民玩太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好安靜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好象我們一直玩鬧到早上都不是真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒玩大貧民了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  大家明天就都回去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天打算怎麼過？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吾輩之辭書無打算一詞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天沒甚麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有些還沒準備充分的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想去一趟畫具店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼過會兒大家一起去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先收拾收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英是明天回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和智花一起回去多好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  我還有稿件的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要在這裡拖到最後關頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊  能順利就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直要到明年才能見面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和山吹高中也要暫時分別了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  各位同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校長好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Merry Xmas
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  嗯  Merry Xmas
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位同學  昨天的Xmas Eve過得好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新學期要讓我看到一副精神飽滿的面容哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祝新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是漫畫裡  笑這麼大聲也要被聽見的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但你想昨天的聖誕老人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天倒還正常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為還是大白天嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聖誕之後就要是年關了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一年過得還真是快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.65,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（自行車少年信也）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,在出發之前還有些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:54.27,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,先請你表演一下自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:56.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  今天是自行車少年信也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  信也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是繼續昨天的節目？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說是自行車少年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或許都是胡謅的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然大的店鋪就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紙張有好多種類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,WATSON紙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,MUSE COTTON
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,MERMAID
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畫筆的種類也好好多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,豬毛的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,馬鬃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,松鼠毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  房東？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挑甚麼呢？做聖誕禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  來買寒假裡用的畫紙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是賀年片嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我在想做一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就開始做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,賀年片總不能到正月裡才做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  要買紙的話還是年後來好些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新年開張的時候是打八折的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:52.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（八折）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,八折嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  下次來買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐的形象是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咩—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才我在那邊碰上房東了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐就是這個了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別從我面前過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說甚麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說黑貓從面前過的話就會倒霉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不過是迷信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼宮子就是這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點快點  吃飯了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你覺得智花是哪一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Snow Doom？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼是這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為又可愛  還閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還一直在一起吃飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為大家一起吃比較開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真想就這麼挨到正月裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要回家去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時就見不著了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐又面臨截稿期限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人的話不覺得寂寞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或許都沒有時間去覺得寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是夠辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.85,0:17:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一個圓圓的剩下了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真快對蛋糕吃膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好個奢侈的發現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是吉野屋老師送來的蛋糕吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒  她自己做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然做到這份上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還附了一張卡片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寫得甚麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新學期還要是一副精神飽滿的樣子喲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有不要忘記作業了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像就這麼吃了有些太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在臉上下刀子還真有點不忍下手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣蛋糕也吃夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回家以後得加油減肥了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？那年糕怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,年節菜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別再說這種東西了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次離開父母一個人生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本還有點惴惴不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有大家在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我過得非常愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙你們很多照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼突然說這個幹甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我本也有些不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是在扯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過嘗試過之後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得或許我挺適合一個人過的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你那自信的根據是哪兒來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過某種意義來說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮是無論在哪兒都能很好地活下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,智花是羡慕我們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不成不成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那丫頭靠不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們自己剛來暖陽莊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不也是受了學姐們不少的照顧嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比如美里學姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  如果是真正意義上的一個人生活的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒有自信能很好地過下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  確實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡又像是一個人過的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎又不像是一個人生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思議的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是真正意義上的一個人生活的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒有自信能不能好好地吃上飯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和你剛才說的不一樣了不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？智花？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說甚麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  謝謝你的聖誕禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？甚麼時候給的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼甚麼？你給的甚麼禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不…那個…沒甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最後還是給她簽名了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算…算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:55.50,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,考試要加油哦  橘文
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？居然是這麼個結局…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺地好象對她做得太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說我是知道的很清楚的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐妹真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好祥和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是個獨生女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很是嚮往兄弟姐妹的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我家裡有個像父母一般的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不大可能有這種情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宮子  這樣吃太難看了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  姐姐生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  明天的準備工作還真是煩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,過年一定要吃個夠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是要減肥的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那別吃太多的年糕喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要又在打盹兒的時候感冒了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要畫賀年片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有些早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祝大家新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新的一年再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好漫長的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細想想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:21:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來這兒也不過一年而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻覺得這裡是自己的家一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己能擁有兩個家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或許也算是很特殊的感覺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:22.41,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,聖誕特刊  冬日的膏狀點心大作戰
